               <p>The Indictment opened by Mr. Fielding. end the Case by Mr. Baldwin.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17850629-62-person561">
                  HENRY
                   HUNTER WILLIAMS
               <interp inst="t17850629-62-person561" type="surname" value="HUNTER WILLIAMS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17850629-62-person561" type="given" value="HENRY"></interp>
