                     <interp inst="t17850629-62-person571" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , there were three more Smiths besides .</p>
               <p>Court. Look into that? - There was a boatswain named 
               <persName id="t17850629-62-person572">
                  John
